   "title": "Next Up: Something with Corn",
   "content": "\u003cspan style=\"font-family: &quot;verdana&quot; , sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: small;\"\u003eDue to yesterday being my birthday, and my refusing to work on that day, this week's first video will be slightly delayed. It should be up later this evening, or tomorrow morning at the latest. Stay tuned!&nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\n\u003cbr /\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-nKra4l5KqmY/V4U6F6WgmVI/AAAAAAAASLI/rD8veAD4T3wGymnHKWTJEo8WvIJZOSXMwCLcB/s1600/IMG_7039.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"\u003e\u003cimg border=\"0\" src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-nKra4l5KqmY/V4U6F6WgmVI/AAAAAAAASLI/rD8veAD4T3wGymnHKWTJEo8WvIJZOSXMwCLcB/s1600/IMG_7039.JPG\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cbr /\u003e",
