   "etag": "\"GtyIIQmNmmUjEA0nwhSqMElCJ1g/dGltZXN0YW1wOiAxNDU4Njk2MzgyODM0Cm9mZnNldDogLTE0NDAwMDAwCg\"",
   "url": "http://foodwishes.blogspot.com/2016/03/roasted-rack-of-lamb-with-strawberry.html",
